item.title: Introduction
item.description: Greeting! This is an introduction to my posts. In this section I will present Deep learning tutorials applied to healtcare and some cool projects that I have been doing around medical imaging and deep learning most often. Some focus on segmentation, classification, object detection models using deep learning for medical imaging
